1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,500
Start on the exact operational screen for this guide.

2
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:05,000
Open System before checking diagnostics.

3
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:07,500
System checks separate workflow problems from integration problems.

4
00:00:07,500 --> 00:00:10,000
Start with backend health and latency before retrying a failed workflow.

5
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:12,500
Check environment, notification, payment, and automation settings for mismatched configuration.

6
00:00:12,500 --> 00:00:15,000
If a payment, message, or booking update failed, check webhooks before asking the customer to repeat it.

7
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,500
Do not keep processing if payments, webhooks, messages, or required integrations are failing.

8
00:00:17,500 --> 00:00:20,000
Use system health when normal workflows do not behave as expected.
